00:42:49.710 --> 00:42:50.630
Sila ay tapat, maaasahan,

00:42:50.630 --> 00:42:51.630
at nakaranas.

00:42:52.310 --> 00:42:53.550
Kung tungkol sa 200 tael ng pilak,

00:42:53.550 --> 00:42:54.810
sapat na para bayaran sila ng isang taon

00:42:54.810 --> 00:42:56.340
at masakop ang halaga ng mga kalakal.

00:42:58.110 --> 00:42:59.190
So, Pingyuan, anong negosyo

00:42:59.190 --> 00:43:00.190
ginagawa ba ng shop na ito?

00:43:00.630 --> 00:43:02.110
Ikaw na ang head manager ngayon.

00:43:02.110 --> 00:43:02.630
Bahala na.

